{"tid":1337184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵男乘客：點解要讓位畀妳　俄狂婦掀裙脫內褲：因為我係女人","createTime":"2019-07-21T08:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T08:40:30.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5130da4299eadd19c7d9efc4a8556f8d1159200f","tid":1337184,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3033411/org/8ea9d72a5fe0fcef2e3289faacb6528a.jpg/uXJ9Ax3R8uN8C7BBfxmjZXRXv3i0I_-Wy14EMcteBDE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3033411%2Forg%2F8ea9d72a5fe0fcef2e3289faacb6528a.jpg%2FuXJ9Ax3R8uN8C7BBfxmjZXRXv3i0I_-Wy14EMcteBDE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b2ef5999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯較一般西方社會較為保守，尤其在性別觀念上，反同相當普遍，社會亦由男性主導，甚至時常批評女性結交外國男友。<br />\n當地一名女子最近在莫斯科地鐵上要求男乘客讓座，遭到拒絕後竟然把自己的裙子掀起及褪下內褲，然後指着下體大喊：「這就是原因，因為我是女人！」令到在場人士嘩然。<br />\n該名女子當日身穿粉紅色裇衫及棕色格仔裙，起初她靜靜地靠著扶手，其後要求一名男子讓座，對方馬上反問：「為甚麼我要讓座給妳？至少應該給我一個好理由」；豈料她突然掀起裙子，並把內褲褪至膝蓋，然後指着下體大喊：「這就是原因，因為我是女人！」<br />\n<br />\n車廂內其他乘客一陣嘩然，狂婦如願獲得座位，但當男事主找到另一個座位時，狂婦卻馬上離開座位，繼續靠在車門邊，以及不斷對該男事主投以厭惡眼神；車門一打開，在月台候車的乘客看到露體狂婦嚇到不敢上車。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱議，有人認為狂婦很可能是女權主義者，但以如此激進的方式要求讓女性得到更合理待遇，恐怕適得其反；另有留言指「該名女子的行為太誇張，很可能有精神問題」、「宣揚女權主義應該要求取消男女差別待遇才對，但妳卻妨礙風化，對其他乘客完全沒有一絲尊重，小心被控告性騷擾」、「這或許是最新叫人讓座的方法」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/351902/%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%8D%E7%95%80%E5%A6%B3-%E4%BF%84%E7%8B%82%E5%A9%A6%E6%8E%80%E8%A3%99%E8%84%AB%E5%85%A7%E8%A4%B2-%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%88%91%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=hottopics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F351902%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%25A6%25B3-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E6%258E%2580%25E8%25A3%2599%25E8%2584%25AB%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A4%25B2-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dhottopics&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=f8cd7d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/351902/%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%8D%E7%95%80%E5%A6%B3-%E4%BF%84%E7%8B%82%E5%A9%A6%E6%8E%80%E8%A3%99%E8%84%AB%E5%85%A7%E8%A4%B2-%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%88%91%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=hottopics</a>"},{"pid":"008afb0b738bdac8b7eaec57afa1058622afc694","tid":1337184,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"理得你除晒衫啦。唔讓就唔讓架啦。"},{"pid":"570ff98e6e3575aa07f0a51ef2c12b2b98979e7a","tid":1337184,"uid":182597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"仲好記得之前有單嘢 有個插隊嘅女人 話自己係女人點解唔可以讓下佢 然後有個地盤佬串鳩佢：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果做女人係有特權嘅話 不如拎你個閪出嚟當八達通咁嘟？ </span>"},{"pid":"189a63aea7482f97608ecd2f69e90d4a9876d15b","tid":1337184,"uid":203543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncRAKfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FncRAKfq.png&h=32034734&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14643c59f83979ad0c561bcff3d2f9311745c938","tid":1337184,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189a63aea7482f97608ecd2f69e90d4a9876d15b","tid":1337184,"uid":203543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncRAKfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%